{"id": 1920, "genre": 1000, "title": "为赶新型月饼营销，商家被逼使了各种招，哪种你不买账？", "description": "冰糖韭菜这种猎奇口味已经不好使了，现在流行的是把月饼做成窝窝头。（题图来自：GIPHY）", "record_count": 9334, "comment_count": 49, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170920141639ZS9dHi1CAloUVFm0.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-24T17:00:40Z", "questions": [{"id": 3007, "title": "为赶新型月饼营销，商家被逼使了各种招，哪种你不买账？", "content": "如今为了赶上新时代的月饼营销，你发现商家们都被逼使了什么招？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 236815, "content": "采用预售模式，给人一种定制的尊贵体验", "image": "img/option/option/20170920144358WoYZpFwGnuLkQclj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236816, "content": "走起粗粮养生路线，比如鹰嘴豆蓝莓月饼、胚芽荏籽五谷月饼", "image": "img/option/option/20170920143002Nwl9GDxsoguOrhct.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236817, "content": "跟网红或IP合作，实现双赢，比如同道大叔星座月饼、故宫月饼", "image": "img/option/option/20170920143159vjdxk0MPDwNVKE3J.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236818, "content": "玩跨界，和音乐平台合作，追求边吃边听歌边思乡的效果", "image": "img/option/option/20170920142325hr6YHO19mKEkTa3j.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236819, "content": "做起了副业，本来做饼干的、卖咖啡的赶着节日推出季节款月饼", "image": "img/option/option/20170920153430VTjUQLNqkOo0JvaI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236820, "content": "主张环保，主打可回收包装材料，或者根本不用盒子的极简主义", "image": "img/option/option/20170920142053kDjQx5SNspPUrFLy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236821, "content": "新型买椟还珠，吃完用盒子做相框、做笔筒、做台灯、做化妆品收纳盒……", "image": "img/option/option/201709201455457agqxNViCbvH9TFK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236822, "content": "科技社交，送人月饼时，对方可以扫码看祝福语、小视频", "image": "img/option/option/201709201421479q8pVlK3hagxbudU.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}